            "showLineNumbers": false,
            "showMiniMap": false
          },
          "content": "## 💾 Core Resource & HPA Monitoring Summary\n\n### **📊 What This Dashboard Shows:**\n\n**✅ Resource Monitoring**\n- Memory & CPU usage by component\n- Resource requests and limits by component\n- **Efficiency ratios** (calculated in dashboard)\n- **Resource headroom** (calculated in dashboard)\n\n**✅ HPA Scaling Intelligence**\n- Current vs desired vs max replicas by component\n- HPA utilization percentages (calculated in dashboard)\n- Scaling event frequency (churn detection)\n\n### **🔧 Recording Rules Required: Only ~18**\n- Phase 1: Basic resource metrics (12 rules)\n- Phase 2: HPA scaling metrics (6 rules)\n- **No efficiency recording rules needed** - calculated on-demand!\n\n### **🎛️ Component Selector**\n**All panels now respect the component selector**, including HPA metrics! You can:\n- View all components (default)\n- Filter to specific components (e.g., only \"distributor\")\n- Compare multiple components side-by-side\n- Focus on problematic components\n\n### **🚀 Smart Approach**\nEfficiency metrics are calculated directly in dashboard queries:\n- `usage / requests` = efficiency ratio\n- `limits - usage` = headroom\n- `current_replicas / max_replicas` = HPA utilization\n\nThis keeps recording rules minimal while providing full insights!",
          "mode": "markdown"
        },
